descriptionHTML:
The Paper Wear watch face is a simple minimalist design based on a layered paper look.

Customizable colours so that you can create the watch face that suits you.
comments: A looker Simply a refreshing bright friendly look. How I wish by pushing the button in the middle would open a small launcher for a few apps, or basic info (Date, weather and such). Then pushing the button again, you come back to the clean beautiful watch Face.
